  <name>Kolf</name>
  <summary>Miniature Golf</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, with a short bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes (warps), among others.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Single and Multi-player (up to ten players) modes</li>
      <li>High scores table</li>
      <li>Dynamic courses</li>
      <li>Third-party courses</li>
      <li>Course editor</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <url type="homepage">http://games.kde.org/game.php?game=kolf</url>
